Commentary Text: Chahal to Gambhir, out Caught by Negi!! Another wicket. It's brought a smile on a couple of faces for RCB. Commentary Text: Aravind to Narine, SIX, there's the fastest IPL fifty. Sunil Narine is the proud owner of that record. If someone had told me that he would be the holder of that record, I would be laughing my guts out, but here he is proving almost everyone wrong. Short of length and Narine goes on his toes and lofts it over long-on. That is a very difficult shot to play and even the best of batsman find it hard, but Narine does it with ease. The KKR dugout are on their feet and GG is leading the applause. For once he has a smile on his face
